snippet.title: Age of Empires IV - "Ottomans and Malians" Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to “Ottomans and Malians,” part of a free update for Age of Empires IV that features two brand new civilizations with innovative strategies for making history your story in both multiplayer and skirmish matches.
 
Lead the mighty Malians of West Africa as one of the richest trading nations of all-time as you focus on strong economic prowess in mining and investing in gold. Or assemble one of the longest lasting empires in history with the Ottoman civilization and its well-trained military force, which features the largest gunpowder siege weapons available – the Great Bombards – mighty cannons that can fell any opponents who stand in your way. 
 
Make history your story as you test your skills with new Art of War challenges and 15 new masteries for each civilization. Free update available October 25, 2022!

Play Age of Empires IV with PC Game Pass now.

Discord: https://discord.gg/ageofempires
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ageofempires
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ageofempiresgame/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ageofempires
